data.description: This 1642 square foot condo home has 3 bedrooms and 3.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 242 Misty Point Ln, Newport News, VA 23603.
data.whatILove:
This is a unique gem nestled in a quiet condo community in the Lee Hall area of Newport News. Completely restored to the studs! Everything is brand new! Beautiful views of Skiffe’s Creek. Freshly painted and move in ready!
1642 sq ft
3 BR, 2.5 bath
Deck and balcony off master bedroom
Gas logs installed
New kitchen appliances (Whirlpool)
Garbage disposal 
Hookups for washer and dryer on first floor
New cabinets and countertops for kitchen and bathrooms
New carpet and composite flooring
New HVAC unit
New Harbor Breeze ceiling fans
New Pella glass front storm door
All new sliding glass doors to deck and balcony
HOA fees ($263.79/month) includes (2) parking spaces, use of clubhouse, grounds maintenance and exterior of unit. 
Serious inquiries only. Must be preapproved.Message if interested. No owner financing or lease to own options. This property is for sale only and not for rent.
